{{multiple issues| {{no footnotes|date=May 2015}} {{notability|Web|date=May 2015}} {{refimprove|date=May 2015}} }} {{Infobox company |name = TestSeek (FMP Publishing AB) |type = [[Privately held company|Private]] |foundation = 2008 |location = [[Göteborg]], [[Sweden]] |key_people = Fredrik Engdahl, CEO, Founder; |industry = [[Review Website]] |num_employees = 5 |homepage = [http://www.testseek.com/ www.testseek.com] }}
'''Testseek''' is a [[review site]] and [[review aggregator]] launched in [[Sweden]] in 2008. Testseek is a global provider of reviews in all major languages to ecommerce portals and retailers to help consumers make better buying decisions.
== History == In the first years, Testseek was mainly focussed on exploiting its own web portal. Gradually the focus has shifted towards business-to-business services, enabling the websites of manufacturers and their channel partners by providing expert and user reviews, and award logos. In 2013, Netvalue (majority owner of [[Open ICEcat]]) joined as shareholder, and helped to expand the customer base.
